text: Anna Matthes (born 5 March 1998) is a German modern pentathlete. She participated at the 2018 World Modern Pentathlon Championships, winning a medal. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:German female modern pentathletes Category:World Modern Pentathlon Championships medalists Category:Modern pentathletes at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics
